description: Name for the load balancing virtual server group. Must begin with an ASCII alphanumeric or underscore (_) character, and must contain only ASCII alphanumeric, underscore, hash (#), period (.), space, colon (:), at (@), equals (=), and hyphen (-) characters. Can be changed after the virtual server is created.  CLI Users: If the name includes one or more spaces, enclose the name in double or single quotation marks (for example, "my lbgroup" or 'my lbgroup').
